      {
        "id": 2475900,
        "name": "Steve Doi",
        "username": "Steve_Doi",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/7ba0ec/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-09-02T22:28:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>If you find her 14\u2019s, give them a try.  The straight village Fixin is very charming and transparent now; the Crais and Arvelets are equally lovely but could use more time.  Her 14 village Vosne was quite nice as well, but in my market, it\u2019s priced competitively with Mugneret-Gibourg and thus I prefer to buy the latter.</p>",
        "post_number": 4,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 7,
