        "created_at": "2018-09-03T15:24:22.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>What little was left of my bottle on day 2 had really tightened up considerably, leading me to believe that PnP was likely a good decision and there is a fairly long life ahead for this wine. That walk-in cellar sounds mighty tempting in this region where the famed domaines are generally not that accessible!</p>",
